Package timeseries.models.arima

Classes for building and forecasting autoregressive integrated moving-average (ARIMA) models.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Arima
    A seasonal autoregressive integrated moving average (ARIMA) model.
    Arima.ModelCoefficients
    Consists of the autoregressive and moving-average coefficients for a seasonal ARIMA model, along with the degrees of differencing and the model mean.
    Arima.ModelCoefficients.Builder
    A builder class for ARIMA model coefficients.
    Arima.ModelOrder
    The order of an ARIMA model, consisting of the number of autoregressive and moving average parameters, along with the degree of differencing and a flag indicating whether or not the model includes a constant, or intercept, term.
    Arima.Simulation
    An ARIMA model simulation.
    Arima.Simulation.Builder  
    ArimaForecast
    A forecast for an ARIMA model.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Arima.FittingStrategy
    The strategy to be used for fitting an ARIMA model.
